text: The Alliance Party is a centrist American political party that was formed in 2018. They are being supported with the American Party of South Carolina, Independence Party of Minnesota, and Independent Party of Connecticut. The party's presidential nominee is Rocky De La Fuente and vice-presidential nominee is Darcy Richardson. ==References== Category:2018 establishments in the United States Category:Political parties in the United States Category:Centrist parties
title: Alliance Party (United States)
